title: >>> TRY Again
body_text:
So after the "failures" of DODGEBALL 75, LXXVI looks to rebound and bring you 2 of the 3 planned happenings.
I.
Who else would make you wait this long? Steve Adams is prepared to shock the dodgeball world with a secret he's been carrying for weeks. You got to love the legend's antics. You just never know what to expect.
II.
So the TOM FUND was met with some problems last week. At LXXVI however, the bucket will debut and Luke will be rewarded at the conclusion of Season 8.
The carnage continues!
QUICK FACT
: DODGEBALL LXXVI takes place on the one year anniversary of DODGEBALL 27. That night, Lauren Winston and Lauren Freda fought to a draw.
